          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1635174606027-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add the <strong>beluga lentils </strong>and<strong> </strong>the <strong>tomato stock </strong>to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Season with a grind of<strong> black pepper </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong>, then cook for 4-5 min or until slightly thickened – this is your <strong>lentil mixture</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
