    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the lentil mixture thickens, return the<strong> drained potatoes</strong> to a low heat with a large knob of <strong>butter</strong>, a splash of <strong>milk </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mash until smooth</p>",
