    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the lentil mixture has thickened, transfer it to an<strong> oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> mashed potato </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until golden brown and bubbling – this is your <strong>lentil</strong> <strong>cottage pie</strong></p>",
